  "prompt": "What are some life lessons I should know by the age of 25?",
  "response": "Here are some important life lessons to know by age 25:\n\n1. Financial Wisdom\n- Start saving early\n- Live below your means\n- Build an emergency fund\n- Learn about investing\n- Understand credit and debt management\n\n2. Personal Growth\n- It's okay to not have everything figured out\n- Continuous learning is essential\n- Embrace failure as a learning opportunity\n- Develop emotional intelligence\n- Prioritize self-improvement\n\n3. Relationships\n- Quality matters more than quantity\n- Communication is key\n- Set healthy boundaries\n- Learn to forgive and let go\n- Choose relationships that support your growth\n\n4. Career\n- Network and build professional relationships\n- Always be willing to learn new skills\n- Take calculated risks\n- Your first job doesn't define your entire career\n- Passion and hard work are more important than perfection\n\n5. Health\n- Develop good habits early\n- Regular exercise is crucial\n- Mental health is as important as physical health\n- Learn to manage stress\n- Prioritize sleep and nutrition\n\n6. Personal Values\n- Know your worth\n- Don't compare yourself to others\n- Stay true to your principles\n- Learn to say no\n- Be authentic\n\n7. Mindset\n- Cultivate a growth mindset\n- Practice gratitude\n- Be adaptable\n- Take responsibility for your life\n- Stay curious and open-minded",
